targets.rawQuery:
with coords as
(
  Select 	 Lat.measure_value::double as Latitude,
			Lng.measure_value::double as Longitude,
  			Lat.vehicleName as vehicleName,
  			Lat.time as time,
   	     	row_number() over (partition by Lat.vehicleName order by Lat.time desc) rn_Lat,
   			row_number() over (partition by Lng.vehicleName order by Lng.time desc) rn_Lng
  from FleetWiseDatabase.FleetWiseTable Lat
      INNER JOIN FleetWiseDatabase.FleetWiseTable Lng on Lat.vehicleName=Lng.vehicleName and Lat.time=Lng.time
  Where 	Lat.measure_name = 'Vehicle.CurrentLocation.Latitude'
      and Lng.measure_name = 'Vehicle.CurrentLocation.Longitude'
)
Select   Latitude,
		Longitude,
        vehicleName,
        time
From coords
Where rn_Lat=1 and rn_Lng=1
order by vehicleName
